    <h3>Welcome to the Mercurialis Inc. Wiki</h3>
    <p>
        Mercurialis Inc. (MINC) is the oldest active a corporation in EVE Online.Whether you're an experienced pilot or new to our ranks, MINC provides a place to learn, contribute, and be part of something bigger. This wiki is here to help you find the information you need about our operations, strategies, and day-to-day activities. It’s a resource for understanding how we work, what we do, and how you can get involved.
    </p>
</div>



